@startuml Backend PostgreSQL persistence

title Backend persistence - PostgreSQL only

component "Program.cs" as Program
component "RecipeDbInitializer" as Initializer
component "RecipeDbContext" as DbContext
component "EfRecipeRepository" as RecipeRepo
component "EfGalleryRepository" as GalleryRepo
database "PostgreSQL" as Postgres

Program --> DbContext : UseNpgsql(connection string)
Program --> RecipeRepo : AddScoped<IRecipeRepository, EfRecipeRepository>
Program --> GalleryRepo : AddScoped<IGalleryRepository, EfGalleryRepository>
Program --> Initializer : startup initialization

RecipeRepo --> DbContext
GalleryRepo --> DbContext
Initializer --> DbContext : Migrate + seed
DbContext --> Postgres

note right of Postgres
Local runtime:
- docker compose db service

Tests:
- Testcontainers PostgreSQL
end note

@enduml
